title: At Emerge 2022, Tampa Bay tech leaders talk trends to watch - St Pete Catalyst
content: At Emerge 2022, Tampa Bay tech leaders talk trends to watch  St Pete Catalyst
description: Dozens of young professionals representing the next generation of Tampa Bay’s technology leaders filled Embarc Collective’s event space Thursday night to hear what three of the leading voices in the region’s tech scene believe are rising trends to watch in 2022. Presented by Tampa Bay Tech's Emerging Leaders Council, "Emerge 2022" is the group's signature [...]
